 * Freescale i.MX53 Quick Start Board
 * In u-boot, this board is known as "MX53LOCO" for some reason.
 *
 * $FreeBSD: stable/10/sys/boot/fdt/dts/arm/imx53-qsb.dts 266365 2014-05-17 22:00:10Z ian $
